1.title: Pups Save an Ostrich/Pups Save the Kitty Rescue Crew
1.plot: Mayor Humdinger makes fake emergencies for his kitties to save so they appear better then the PAW Patrol. The Wingnuts get a new pet ostrich, but it gets lost on the trip home.

2.title: Pups Save Hum-Go/Pups Save Big Paw
2.plot: When an ancient relic goes missing from Carlos' archeological dig, Ryder assigns Tracker and Skye to track down the mysterious creature that may have taken it. Mayor Humdinger pretends to break his toe in order to win a race!

3.title: Pups Save a Sunken Sloop/Pups Save a Wiggly Whale
3.plot: Sid the Pirate and his First Mate Arrby have taken the sunken sloop! A wiggling whale has knocked the diving bell upside down. It's stuck in the sand at the bottom of the ocean, with Cap'n Turbot and Francois inside!

4.title: Pups Go for Gold/Pups Save a High Flying Skye
4.plot: A thunder storm causes a blackout in Adventure Bay. Afraid, Corny runs away from Farmer Al's Farm. Skye finds him, but the pups need to light the way to get them home safely! Uncle Otis and his Golden Nugget are hurtling down Jake's Mountain in a runaway mine car!

5.title: Pups Save a Cat Burglar/Pups Save an Extreme Lunch
5.plot: Daring Danny X is performing a new stunt! He is harnessed over a canyon eating an Extreme Lunch when the wind blows him upside down! It's Pie Swap Day in Adventure Bay!

6.title: Pups Save a Soggy Farm/Pups Save a Flying Diving Bell
6.plot: Farmer Al's farm is flooded! The PAW Patrol need to rescue him, his animals, and get to the bottom of what's causing the flood! Francois and Turbot discover an underwater volcano.

7.title: Pups Save the Butterflies/Pups Save an Underground Chicken
7.plot: Chickaletta is stuck on a runaway drone and mysterious butterflies are causing chaos all around Adventure Bay! The statue of Chickaletta has been stolen!

8.title: Pups save a Bookmobile/Pups Save a Heady Humdinger
8.plot: Everest and the kids of Adventure Bay visit Ms. Marjorie's Bookmobile to see what new books she's brought! Meanwhile - Maynard decides to take the Bookmobile for a wild ride! Mayor Humdinger has been carving his face in the cliffs of Adventure Bay.

9.title: Pups Save their Pirated Sea Patroller
9.plot: The ferris wheel has been stolen by Sid the Pirate and Arrby. The pups set out to bring it back to Adventure Bay! However, Sid comes up with an even more sneaky plan: to steal the Sea Patroller!

10.title: Pups Save the PawPaws/Pups Save a Popped Top
10.plot: Carlos and Tracker make PawPaw juice with the PAW Patrol when they find out Mayor Goodway and Chickaletta are in trouble. The top of Farmer's Al's silo has been knocked off, and he needs help saving his corn crop.

11.title: Ultimate Rescue: Pups save the Royal Kitties
11.plot: The Royal Kitties are kidnapped on their way to Adventure Bay for a special visit. Ryder needs all the pups to help Chase investigate this case in an Ultimate Police Rescue!

12.title: Pups save the Snowshoeing Goodways/Pups Save A Duck Pond
12.plot: When Mayor Goodway and the twins are late getting back from a snowshoeing, Jake and Everest call the PAW Patrol to search for them. When water in the duck pond mysteriously drains out, it's up to the PAW Patrol to find out what's happening!

13.title: Sea Patrol: Pups save Tilly Turbot/Pups save an Upset Elephant
13.plot: The PAW Patrol must rescue Cap'n Turbot and Francois' Grandma Tilly after she rides off on a dolphin. Carlos and Tracker call the PAW Patrol to help solve the mystery of a rumbling sound that's upsetting the jungle elephants.

14.title: Ultimate Rescue: Pups Save the Tigers
14.plot: When searching for elusive rumble top tigers, the Turbots fall into a cave deep inside a volcano. The PAW Patrol does a paratrooper style rescue from Skye's Ultimate copter in this Ultimate Aviator Rescue!

15.title: Rocky Saves Himself/Pups and the Mystery of the Driverless Snowcat
15.plot: Daring Danny's new remote control accidentally takes control of Everest's SnoCat and all the vehicles in Adventure Bay! Rocky must rescue himself when he has been stranded on an island full of trash by Mayor Humdinger.

16.title: Mission Paw: Pups Save a Royal Concert/Pups Save the Princess' Pals
16.plot:

17.title: Pups save the Movie Monster
17.plot: Envious Mayor Humdinger tries to draw the Adventure Bay Monster Movie production to Foggy Bottom by commandeering the mechanical movie monster. But he can't control the fireball-breathing robot. All the pups join Marshall on this Ultimate Fire Rescue!

18.title: Pups Save the Trick-or-Treaters/Pups Save an Out of Control Mini Patrol
18.plot: It's Halloween in Adventure Bay, and a mysterious kid in a giant spider costume is taking all the treats from the trick-or-treaters.

19.title: Pups and the Werepuppy!/Pups Save a Sleepwalking Mayor
19.plot: Rocky goes missing at Uncle Otis's cabin, and the PAW Patrol needs to solve the mystery of the Werepuppy!

25.title: Ultimate Rescue: Pups Save a Runaway Stargazer
25.plot: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

26.title: Pups Save Ace's Birthday Surprise/Pups Save a Tower of Pizza
26.plot:

1.title: Pups Make a Splash/Pups Fall Festival
1.plot: Cap'n Turbot's boat has crashed into a rock, so Ryder and the PAW Patrol must leap into action.

2.title: Pups Save the Sea Turtles/Pups and the Very Big Baby
2.plot: The PAW Patrol pups are playing on the beach when they discover sea turtle hatchlings. Later, Cap'n Turbot needs help moving a beached baby whale back out into the bay.

3.title: Pups and the Kitty-tastrophe/Pups Save the Train
3.plot: Ryder and the PAW Patrol rescue a lost kitty from the bay, but who will save them from all the mayhem she causes?/Ryder, Rubble, and Rocky call in Chase to help them free Katie and Cali's train from a rockslide!

4.title: Pup Pup Boogie/Pups in a Fog
4.plot: The PAW Patrol must work quickly to fix the tracks and remove a train car at the train station before the next train comes in. Later, Cap'n Turbot is lost at sea when a deep fog rolls in.

5.title: Pup, Pup, Goose/Pup, Pup and Away
5.plot: Marshal gets a new BFF when a gosling he names "Fuzzy" takes a liking to him. /When Mayor Goodway accidentally takes off in a hot air balloon, Ryder and the Paw Patrol must make a dramatic rescue to save her and win the race!

6.title: Pups and the Snow Monster/Pups on Ice
6.plot: Ryder and the PAW Patrol need to rescue Alex on Jakes mountain./The pups find strange footprints in the snow on the mountain outside Adventure Bay. Everyone thinks it's a "snow monster" and it's scaring the skiers away.

7.title: Pups Save the Circus/Pup a Doodle Do
7.plot: Ellie the baby elephant has escaped from the circus train. Mayor Goodway's purse chicken has gone missing.

8.title: Pups Pit Crew/Pups Fight Fire
8.plot: Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to rescue Alex when he takes off on his new "super trike"./Marshall proves he is a true hero when he stops to put out a real fire on the beach during a race against the clock for a trophy.

9.title: Pups Get a Rubble/Pups Save a Walrus
9.plot: We see a flashback of how Rubble became a member of the Paw Patrol!/When Wally the Walrus gets tangled in an old fishing net, Ryder and the Paw Patrol need to get him to the surface and back to shore safely.

10.title: Pups Save the Bay/Pups Save a Goodway
10.plot: Ryder and the PAW Patrol clean up a small oil spill in the water near Adventure Bay. /When Adventure Bay's famous statue ends up at the bottom of the Bay, Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to help Mayor Goodway bring it back!

11.title: Pups Save Christmas
11.plot: When Santa's Sleigh crashes and the reindeer run off - Ryder and the PAW PATROL have to help Santa finish delivering presents and save Christmas!

12.title: Pups and the Ghost Pirate
12.plot: It's Halloween. Cap'n Turbot has decorated an old wreck as a pirate ship for a town party. When the ship mysteriously heads out to sea captained by a "ghost" Ryder and the Paw Patrol must save the ship and discover the ghost.

13.title: Pups Save the Bunnies/Puptacular
13.plot: Carrots are disappearing around Adventure Bay, so Ryder and the pups try to figure out why./Katie is excited to be entering one of the PAW Patrol pups into a puppy grooming competition "Puptacular" in the next town.

14.title: Pups Save the Treats/Pups Get a Lift
14.plot: Mr. Porters van full of puppy food slides on the ice near the shore; Ryder and the PAW Patrol must save the day!/Katie and her cat Cali are on the chair lift when it stops leaving them above the ski hill with no way to get down!

15.title: Pups Save a Hoedown/Pups Save Alex
15.plot: It's Adventure Bay Western Days, when a herd of cows escape from a train at the railway station!/When their friend Alex decides he wants to be a member of the PAW Patrol the PUPS and Ryder let him come along for the ride.

16.title: Pups Save a School Day/Pups Turn on the Lights
16.plot: Ryder and the PAW Patrol pups set out to find a missing backpack./A storm causes the power to go out on Chase's birthday.

17.title: Pups Save a Pool Day/Circus Pup Formers
17.plot: It's a hot day and the pups head for the water park - but the pool is empty! Paw Patrol to the rescue. /When the animals don't show up in time for the Circus to start; Ryder and the Paw Patrol step in to help.

18.title: Pups Save a Super Pup/Pups Save Ryder's Robot
18.plot: When Ryder's Robot Pup breaks and starts going wild around Adventure Bay, it takes the whole Paw Patrol to help Ryder find it.

19.title: Pups Go All Monkey/Pups Save a Hoot
19.plot: When Mandy the monkey escapes from her cage on the train, Ryder and the PAW Patrol are lead on a wild chase through Adventure Bay! During a bad wind storm, Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to save an Owl trapped in a blown over tree and reunite her with "Little Hootie", her baby.

20.title: Pups Save a Bat/Pups Save a Toof!
20.plot: A baby Bat decides to take a nap hanging from the Town Hall's bell and Mayor Goodway can't ring it. Ryder and the Pups attempt to rescue the bat quietly so it doesn't wake up, but it does and causes trouble around town. It's up to Ryder and the Pups to get the Bat and return her to her Bat cave. Alex is afraid to go to the dentist, so Chase and the PAW Patrol work together to show Alex that fears can be overcome.

21.title: Pups Save the Easter Egg Hunt
21.plot: It's Adventure Bay's annual Easter Egg hunt and the pups are helping Mayor Goodway with the egg decorating. Th+e hunt for a very special egg leads Ryder and the Paw Patrol on an exciting adventure!

22.title: Pups Save the Camping Trip/Pups Turtle Trouble
22.plot: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

23.title: Pups and the Beanstalk/Pups Save the Turbots
23.plot: Francois wants to help Cap'n Turbot take a picture of a rare bird.

24.title: Pups and the Lighthouse Boogie!/Pups Save Ryder
24.plot: Mayor Goodway and Alex take a rowboat out into the bay to get a closer look at a baby whale. A storm is approaching though and the rowboat drifts out of control towards the sea. It's up to the PAW Patrol to rescue them! While out on a hike Ryder discovers Garby the goat stuck on a cliff edge! He attempts to rescue Garby but gets stranded in the process. He calls the pups for help but drops his Pup Pad down the cliff side! Now the Pups have to save Ryder - all on their own.

25.title: Pups Great Race/Pups Take the Cake
25.plot: It's Adventure Bay Race Day and the pups are about to race each other all across the town to see who is the fastest pup. One other competitor unexpectedly shows up though, Alex in his super trike! Mr.Porter enters a cake competition and needs Ryder and the pups to help him bake the biggest and tastiest cake. The race is on to get their cake baked and to the competition on time!

26.title: Pups and the Pirate Treasure
26.plot: Cap'n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern that was once a pirate's hideout. When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete treasure map. The adventure is on as the pups follow clues to find the missing map pieces, and eventually to a sunken pirate treasure!

1.title: Pups Save the Penguins/Pups Save a Dolphin Pup
1.plot: Someone has been swiping fish off Cap'n Turbot's boat, so he calls Ryder and the PAW Patrol to help investigate. Using his new SPY GEAR, Chase inspects the boat and heads below deck where he discovers it's a group of pesky Penguins! Now the Pups have to catch the slippery suspects and find a way to get them back to the South Pole!

2.title: Pups Save a Flying Frog/Pups Save the Space Alien
2.plot: Marshall's new pet frog, Smiley, is going to be in a jumping contest! The only problem is that during a practice run Smiley jumps right into Skye's helicopter and it takes off! Now Skye and the Pups have to save Smiley, and get him to the competition in time!

3.title: Pups Save a Jake/Pups Save the Parade
3.plot: Jake and Chase go deep cave spelunking when Jake ends up getting his ankle stuck between some fallen rocks! Ryder, Rubble with his new JACKHAMMER, and Marshall with his new FIRST MEDICAL RESPONSE GEAR need to get to the cave right away and save Jake! Adventure Bay Parade Day goes awry when Alex puts too many balloons on Katie's bathtub float. It literally "floats" away, and with Cali and Chickaletta inside!

4.title: Pups Save the Diving Bell/Pups Save the Beavers
4.plot: Cap'n Turbot and Francois go deep sea diving to snap a picture of a rare sea slug - the only problem is their diving bell ends up stuck, and then the propeller fin breaks at the bottom of the bay! The pups must help, and they have just the right vehicle - Zuma's new submarine! A bad storm washes away Chompy the Beaver's dam, so he starts chomping on wood products all around Adventure Bay!

5.title: The New Pup
5.plot: Ryder surprises the pups with a new mobile lookout so they can save the day elsewhere.

6.title: Pups Save a Show/Pups Save a Ghost
6.plot: A mysterious Ghost is causing havoc around the Lookout at night. The Pups and Chase in his new spy gear set up a stakeout to bust it, but discover that it's not a ghost after all, its Marshall sleepwalking.

7.title: Pups Save a Herd/Pups and the Curse of the Mandy
7.plot: Farmer Al calls Ryder and needs help to fix his fence and herd all the sheep. Now the Pups have to fix the fence and Chase has to herd all the sheep in time to make it to the competition.

8.title: Pups Save a Big Freeze/Pups Save a Basketball Game
8.plot: The PAW Patrol has to help everybody that has been affected by the ice storm The PAW Patrol and Ryder have to play a basketball against Mayor Humdinger's basketball team.

9.title: Pups Save a Wedding/Pups Save an Ace
9.plot: The Pups help Farmer Yumi prepare for her wedding day after a storm blew the barn apart; Skye and the Pups must save her famous stunt pilot and her plane before it sinks into the ocean.

10.title: Pups Save a Talent Show/Pups Save the Corn Roast
10.plot: It's Adventure Bay Talent Show Day! When the mayor is afraid there won't be enough acts, the super talented Pups can definitely help out! When Chickaletta gets trapped in a Corn Field Maze, the PAW Patrol races to the rescue!

11.title: Pups Leave Marshall Home Alone/Pups Save the Deer
11.plot: With the other pups at parachute training, Marshall must get a group of loose kittens back all by himself. But he has the help of the other pups' packs! Ryder and the PAW Patrol rescue a family of deer stuck on sippery ice!

12.title: Pups Save the Queen Bee/Pups Save the Parrot
12.plot: The PAW Patrol heads to the jungle to help their friend Carlos find his lost parrot, Mateo! When the PAW Patrol discovers a beehive in Cap'n Turbot's lighthouse, Ryder and the pups must work together to find the bees a new home.

13.title: Pups Save a Mer-Pup
13.plot: When the Pups and Cap'n Turbot camp out under the very rare Magical Mer Moon, magical things begin to happen. Lured by the mystical Mer-Pup song, the PAW Patrol is transformed into Mer -Pups themselves!

14.title: Pups Save an Elephant Family/Pups and the Mischievous Kittens
14.plot: Francois and Cap'n Turbot want to take a photo of an elephant family, but only one elephant can be found. A group of upset kittens make a mess in Adventure Bay. Pups to the rescue.

15.title: Pups Save a Stowaway/Pups Save a Friend
15.plot: When Marshall decides to take a break from the PAW Patrol, the pups jump into action to bring him back! When the pups find a stowaway on their trip to the Icy Tundra, they must rescue a run-away kitty on a run-away Snow Cat!

16.title: Pups' Adventures in Babysitting/Pups Save the Fireworks
16.plot: Mayor Goodway calls on the Paw Patrol to rescue her twin neice and nephew from a tree, and then twin sit for the day! Expecting the fireworks for Adventure Bay Day, Mayor Goodway receives a package of piglets after a mix-up!

17.title: Pups and the Ghost Cabin/Pups Save a Sniffle
17.plot: A sick day for the PAW Patrol? While Rubble and Ryder search for Farmer Al's runaway pigs, Marshall cares for his sniffly pup pals! First Rubble's lunch disappears, then Jake's lunchbox walks away! Could it be a... ghost?!

18.title: Pups Save an Adventure/Pups Save a Surprise
18.plot: Alex is working towards getting his Action Scouts Fire Safety Badge, and who better to help him learn all about Fire Safety than Marshall and the Paw Patrol! It's just another regular day in Adventure Bay as the Paw Patrol is called to duty. After a day of rescues, the pups notice that City Hall has been decorated for a big celebration. Surprise! It's Paw Patrol Appreciation Day!

19.title: Pup-Fu!
19.plot: The pups are learning the ancient art of Pup-Fu! They'll need it to get back Sensei Farmer Yumi's ancient martial arts scroll, after Mayor Humdinger's Kit-tastrophe Crew use their Cat-Jitsu skills to steal it!

20.title: Pups Save an Iron Mayor/Pups Find an Outlaw's Loot
20.plot: It's the annual Mayor's Race! Mayor Goodway is determined to give it her best, while Mayor Humdinger is planning his most devious cheating scheme yet. Ryder helps Mayor Goodway sort through the old cabin of Outlaw Wild Wilbur when they come across a map for his buried treasure. Mayor Humdinger snatches the map and runs off to find the loot for himself.

21.title: Pups Save a Big Bone/Pups Save Walinda
21.plot: In "Pups Save a Big Bone," Cap'n Turbot and Francois try to uncover a dinosaur bone. In "Pups Save Walinda," Cap'n Turbot is worried when his best friend Wally the Walrus does not show up at the PAW Patrol's Wally Appreciation Day party.

22.title: Pups Save a Floundering Francois/Pups Save the Pop-Up Penguins
22.plot: Francois is lost at sea after he takes Cap'n Turbot's boat to go whale-watching. Stowaway penguins have scattered around Adventure Bay. Time to call the PAW Patrol.

23.title: Pups Save a Snowboard Competition/Pups Save a Chicken of the Sea
23.plot: In "Pups Save a Snowboard Competition," the pups must help out when a snowboarding course is buried by snow. In "Pups Save a Chicken of the Sea," Seabee (Cap'n Turbot's talking computer) accidentally sends Chickaletta to the seafloor.

24.title: Pups Save a Pizza/Pups Save Skye
24.plot: Alex and Mr. Porter are delivering pizza dough for a big party when the van spins out of control. Pups to the rescue! Skye is on her way to Jake's Mountain when she crash lands in the snow. Ryder calls Everest to save the day!

25.title: Pups Save the Woof and Roll Show/Pups Save an Eagle
25.plot: When a big pop star comes to town, a storm blows the whole town apart, including the stage! Can the PAW Patrol save the day? While out in the woods, the pups rescue an eagle caught in twine and tied to her own nest.

26.title: Pups Bark with Dinosaurs
26.plot: The pups and Cap'n Turbot head out to the jungle to look for dinosaur fossils.

1.title: Pups Find a Genie/Pups Save a Tightrope Walker
1.plot: In "Pups Find a Genie," Rubble finds a genie's jack-in-the-box. Then, in "Pups Save a Tightrope Walker," Francois prepares to walk a tightrope from the top of Adventure Bay Bridge to the Lookout.

2.title: Pups Save the Soccer Game/Pups Save a Lucky Collar
2.plot: In "Pups Save the Soccer Game," Ryder and the pups are called in to play in a soccer match. In "Pups Save a Lucky Collar," Marshall receives a supposedly lucky collar that he thinks will help him in rescuing an owl with Cap'n Turbot.

3.title: Air Pups
3.plot: Cap'n Turbot and Francois visit Volcano Island as part of a monkey communication expedition, but are put in danger when the volcano erupts. The PAW Patrol uses their new Air Patroller to rescue the two, along with a family of monkeys.

4.title: Pups Save Friendship Day
4.plot: While celebrating Friendship Day, the pups spring into action to prevent Mayor Humdinger from ruining Adventure Bay's reputation as the friendliest town on the map.

5.title: Pups Save Alex's Mini-Patrol/Pups Save a Lost Tooth
5.plot: In "Pups Save Alex's Mini-Patrol," the pups receive unexpected help from another patrol. In "Pups Save a Lost Tooth," the pups try to locate a lost tooth, which ends up being taken out to sea after it falls into Cap'n Turbot's fish bucket.

6.title: Pups Save the Daring Danny X/Pups in a Fix
6.plot: When a boy named Danny sees Ryder perform an incredible stunt during a rescue, it inspires him to become a daredevil. Changing his name to Daring Danny X, the boy attempts to jump 10 cars with his ATV.

7.title: Pups Save a Goldrush/Pups Save the PAW Patroller
7.plot: Mayor Humdinger and his Catastrophe Crew hijack the PAW Patroller. Ryder and the Paw Patrol give chase to the vehicle.

8.title: Pups Save a Dragon/Pups Save the Three Little Pigs
8.plot: The town play is sure to be a hit with Katie as a princess and Marshall playing as the back half of a dragon.

9.title: Pups Save Apollo/Pups Save the Hippos
9.plot: In "Pups Save the Hippos," the pups spring into action when three hippos knock down a circus tent. In "Pups Save Apollo," Rubble falls asleep while watching an Apollo the Super-Pup marathon on TV.

10.title: Pups Save the Polar Bears/A Pup in Sheep's Clothing
10.plot: The Pups are delighted to be spending the whole day watching an Apollo-Super-Pup marathon on TV. When everyone but Rubble falls asleep, Apollo gets captured by his greatest foe - The Spider King.

11.title: Pups Save a School Bus/Pups Save the Songbirds
11.plot: When all the tires on the Adventure Bay school bus blow out, Rocky has to help repair them. Meanwhile, the kids still need to get to school, so Ryder volunteers to use the Paw Patroller.

12.title: Pups Save Old Trusty/Pups Save a Pony
12.plot: Ryder has a mystery on his hands when Adventure Bay is thrown into chaos by jets of water gushing up all over town.

13.title: All Star Pups!/Pups Save Sports Day
13.plot: In "All Star Pups", the PAW Patrol competes against a team of monkeys in a charity game. In "Pups Save Sports Day", the pups find a way to incorporate winter events in their Sports Day celebration.

14.title: Tracker Joins the Pups!
14.plot: Ryder admits a big-eared pup named Tracker into the PAW Patrol after Tracker performs a rescue in the jungle.

15.title: Parroting Pups/Merpups Save the Turbots
15.plot: In "Merpups Save the Turbots", a sea slug gets in the way of Cap'n Turbot and Francois' plan to take photos of magical merpups. In "Parroting Pups", Rocky loses his voice and has trouble using his pup pack.

16.title: Pups Save a Robo-Saurus/Pups Save a Film Festival
16.plot: The pups have to return a robotic dinosaur to its owners after it disappears in the desert. Everyone in Adventure Bay is entering a film festival and the pups decide to make a superhero movie.

17.title: Pups Save a Stinky Flower/Pups Save a Monkey-naut
17.plot: In "Pups Save a Stinky Flower", Rocky gets a brand new tugboat. He uses it to transport a smelly plant back to its owner. In "Pups Save a Monkey-naut", Ryder is fishing with Rocky and Zuma until they spot a monkey astronaut's spaceship.

18.title: Pups Bear-ly Save Danny/Pups Save the Mayor's Tulips
18.plot: The pups must lure hungry bears back to their den after a reckless boy attracts the bears' attention. Rocky and Chase work to protect the mayor's tulip garden so that they can be entered in a contest.

19.title: Pups Get Growing/Pups Save a Space Toy
19.plot: Pups Get Growing/Pups Save a Space Toy: Fertilizer causes Yumi's crops to sprout humongous veggies. The Paw Patrol draws a message on Farmer Al's field to let their friends the Space Aliens know the pups found their lost toy!

20.title: Pups in a Jam/Pups Save a Windsurfing Pig
20.plot: It's the annual Jamboree Jamfest, but all of the fruit is carried off by ants! Zuma is on a wacky windsurfing water rescue after Cornelius the pig decides to go for a ride on a borrowed windsurfing board.

21.title: Pups Save the Gliding Turbots/Pups Save a Plane
21.plot: When Francois and Cap'n Turbot become stranded on a remote island, Ryder and the pups fly in to the rescue. It's a double daring mid-air rescue as Mayor Goodway's first flying lesson goes sideways.

22.title: Pups Get Skunked/Pups and a Whale of a Tale
22.plot: When Everest gets sprayed by a skunk, the pups delicately try to tell her she needs a bath! The pups put a new spin on freeze tag after they fly far north to help free a baby whale.

23.title: The Pups' Winter Wonder Show
23.plot: The Adventure Bay Snow-Show is in danger of being a No-Show when Mayor Humdinger escapes with the feature act, Cap'n Turbot's performing penguins. It's up to the Paw Patrol to return the penguins so that the show can go on!

24.title: Pups Save a Giant Plant/Pups Get Stuck
24.plot: Mayor Goodway's gesture of goodwill gift grows wildly out of control when it's planted in the wrong place. Time for a transplant! Metal mayhem ensues when Marshall's Fire Truck becomes mysteriously magnetized.

25.title: Pups Raise the PAW Patroller/Pups Save the Crows
25.plot: Daring Danny's at it again! Luckily the Pups raise their rig after Danny sinks the Paw Patroller. Ryder and the Pups pair up with Alex and his mini patrol to retrieve mysteriously missing items.

26.title: Pups Save Floating Friends/Pups Save a Satellite
26.plot: The aliens' spaceship is on the fritz and shooting out anti-gravity rays. A satellite is out of orbit and falling towards Adventure Bay!

1.title: Pups Save a Blimp/Pups Save the Chili Cook-Off
1.plot: Capn' Turbot's weather blimp is taken by Mayor Humdinger, who plans to use it to change the weather in Foggy Bottom. Mr. Porter's stove explodes right before the chili cook-off!

2.title: Pups Save a Teeny Penguin/Pups Save the Cat Show
2.plot: Everest and Jake try to rescue a little penguin and end up floating out to sea. Katie's kittens are all covered in mud and running amuck! If they're not rounded up, the Cat Show will be ruined.

3.title: Pups Save a Playful Dragon/Pups Save the Critters
3.plot: Buddy, the playful dragon from one of Alex's books, gets out and the pups need to get him back. Francois's trailer unhooked, and all of his critters have gotten loose!

4.title: Mission PAW
4.plot: Sweetie tries to steal the crown jewels to become the Queen of Barking burg. It's up to PAW Patrol to stop her.

5.title: Pups Save a Sleep Over/Pups Save the Carnival
5.plot: Farmer Al's animals go missing during a sleepover. Cornelius has escaped from the pig ride at the carnival, and the prizes have gone missing too!

6.title: Pups Save a Wild Ride/Pups Save Jake's Cake
6.plot: Ryder and the Pups need to help get a surprise birthday ice cream cake up to Jake's cabin. Alex and Daring Danny X are snowboarding right for Risky Ridge and need help from the PAW Patrol.

7.title: Pups Save Monkey-Dinger/Pups Bust a Royal Ghost
7.plot: The Princess thinks she's seen a ghost, and PAW Patrol needs to get to the bottom of it. While on a safari the Mayor steals a magic mask which instantly turns his actions into those of a monkey.

8.title: Pups Save the Flying Food/Pups Save a Ferris Wheel
8.plot: Mr. Porter's delivery drones have gone out of control, and now they are air-dropping food everywhere! Mayor Humdinger steals Adventure Bay's Ferris Wheel.

9.title: Pups Save a Dude Ranch Danny/Pups Save a Sleepwalking Bear
9.plot: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

10.title: Pups Save the Royal Throne
10.plot: Sweetie plans to steal the actual royal throne, so she can rule.

11.title: Pups Save Big Hairy/Pups Save a Flying Kitty
11.plot: Pups need to lure a big ape onto the PAW Patroller so they can take him back to the jungle. Skye Kitty gets stuck beside an eagle's nest and needs help getting down.

12.title: Pups Save the Sensei/Pups Party with Bats
12.plot: Bats are drawn from their cave by DJ Rubble's new dance track. A wind storm threatens unsuspecting Marshall and Sensei Yumi.

13.title: Pups Save a Baby Octopus
13.plot: A baby Octopus gets separated from its mother and sinks the Flounder. Sea Patrol needs to save the day!

14.title: Pups Save Tiny Marshall/Pups Save the Runaway Kites
14.plot: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

15.title: Pups Chill Out/Pups Save Farmer Alex
15.plot: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

16.title: Pups Save a Shark/Pups Save the Pier
16.plot: In hopes to have the whole beach to himself, Humdinger makes a robotic shark to scare everyone away. The pier could fall into the water due to a broken support post. Pups to the rescue!

17.title: Save a Good Mayor/Save a Space Rock
17.plot: Everest, the Turbots, and a Space Rock get trapped in a cave. Mayor Gooway goes missing, and Mayor Humdinger causes havoc in Adventure Bay.

18.title: Pups Save a City Kitty/Pups Save a Cloud-Surfer
18.plot: Cali gets lost in the woods. Daring Danny X's harness loosens while kite-surfing.

19.title: Pirate Pups to the Rescue
19.plot: Carlos and Tracker get stranded on an island in the search for buried treasure.

20.title: Pups Save the Mail/Pups Save a Frog Mayor
20.plot: The postman's truck gets stuck in the mud, and the mail gets stuck in a tree! Mayor Goodway turns into a frog!

21.title: Pups Save the Runaway Turtles/Pups Save the Shivering Sheep
21.plot: Daring Danny X accidently drives off with turtle eggs! Farmer Al's sheep run away, and Mayor Humdinger's kittens go missing

22.title: Pups Save a Frozen Flounder/Pups Save a Narwhal
22.plot: Cap'n Turbot's boat gets frozen in the Arctic Ice.The pups use the Sea Patroller to help guide a lost narwhal back home.

23.title: Pups Save Chicken Day/Pups Save Luke Stars
23.plot: Katie is going to perform her contest-winning song with Luke Stars! But Luke Stars gets stuck on a mountain ledge on his way to Adventure Bay. Chickaletta goes missing on Chicken Day! The PAW Patrol have to find her to save the festivites.

24.title: Pups Save Francois the Penguin/Pups Save Daring Danny and His Hippo
24.plot: Francois and a baby penguin get caught on the other side of a carvasse. Daring Danny wants a cool pet of his own, so he can't believe his luck when a stray baby hippo finds him.

25.title: Pups Save Baby Humdinger/Pups Save a Pinata
25.plot: Tracker has a dream that Mayor Humginder turns into a baby! Now it's up to the pups to find the special coconuut to reverse the spell. Alex is hosting a fun party in Adventure Bay but is heartbroken when his special pinata mysteriously disappears.

26.title: Pups Save Puplantis
26.plot: Sid Swashbuckle the Pirate and his first pup mate Arrby steal the giant pearl-making shell that gives Puplantis its magic.

imdb.title: PAW Patrol
plot: Led by a boy named Ryder, a team of six playful rescue dogs use their individual talents to protect the seaside town of Adventure Bay. The pups are occasionally joined by newer helpers: Cap'n Turbot, Robo-Dog, Everest, and Tracker.::Contributor
